      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind a bit of character. The engine runs well and the car is mechanically sound for regular commutes, though you may notice some minor interior wear and a few cosmetic blemishes on the exterior, including small dings and some paint fading. The tires have decent tread left, but the suspension is starting to show its age and may need attention in the coming year. It\u2019s an honest, functional car that gets the job done without the price tag of a showroom model.",
