    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total stunner. This car is in pristine, showroom condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one, so it still looks and smells brand new! It drives like an absolute dream with zero issues. If you're looking for something that\u2019s been meticulously cared for and is ready for the road, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love for this to go to a great new home!",
      "price": 43500.0,
