    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that stands in breathtaking, showroom-ready condition. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster, entirely free from swirls, stone chips, or blemishes, while the alloy wheels remain in pristine, uncurbed condition. Stepping inside, the cabin is a testament to meticulous care; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no creasing or wear, and the interior still retains its original new-car scent. Every technological feature and electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, having been maintained with an 'open checkbook' philosophy and supported by a comprehensive, up-to-date service history. It has been exclusively climate-controlled garaged and never driven in inclement weather. This is a rare opportunity to own a flawless example that satisfies even the most rigorous inspection.",
