      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car is in incredible shape\u2014I\u2019ve babied it from day one and it still has that 'new car' feel! It\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously detailed, and drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for something that's basically flawless and ready for the road, this is the one! I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
